1. 385g flour
2. 220g water
3. 2.2 table spoon sunflover oil
4. 1.1 tea spoon of Salt
5. cover the dough and 20min rest

Use 80gram parts of dough for roll out in aproxm 25cm radius lavash, in resault after fried should be 20cm lavash

6. Fry for 1 min every side, when fry finished lubricate with water every side of Lavash (use pastry brush or spray) 
Task: try cut on 90gram parts of dough
